    "The performance of this model was extensively assessed by considering various assessment measures.",
    "By comparing the CNN+EfficientNetV2B3 model with other breast cancer detection techniques, the CNN +EfficientNetV2B3 model obtained high accuracy and proved its superiority.",
    "The maximum accuracy was reached by combining the CNN with the EfficientNetV2B3 model, data augmentation approaches, powerful optimization algorithms, and thorough assessment metrics.",
    "The proposed hybrid model uses transfer learning to combine the strengths of two pre-trained models, MobileNet [30] and DenseNet121 [31], for more robust breast cancer classification.",
